{"tid":22624,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東南亞三十日","createTime":"2016-12-04T14:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T07:33:26.000Z","uid":22444,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f934f93663431cd29eb165510b04149be78ff47","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"自己本身好鍾意去旅行，礙於窮撚一名，冇乜機會旅行唯有得閒上下高登睇遊記。但自從HKG+冇咗，嚟咗LIHKG，發覺冇乜人係旅遊台抗遊記。暑假去咗東南亞fing咗三十日，本身冇諗過打遊記，但我希望打完會吸引到更多人一齊分享自己嘅旅遊經歷。<br />\n<br />\n主要路程：<br />\nIndonesia &gt; Malaysia &gt; Cambodia &gt; Thailand &gt; Laos &gt; China &gt; HK<br />\n<br />\n總括呢個旅遊係走馬看花，因為我太貪心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。所以呢篇遊記應該偏向資訊性（希望有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。歡迎問問題。"},{"pid":"edf591f9279659b710c0b789303558cf14ed814f","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/221938_6b92831a97578d02198c24933eaa3292.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F221938_6b92831a97578d02198c24933eaa3292.jpg&h=526de82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBali (Indonesia)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhVfxVd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhVfxVd.jpg&h=98d82cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEast Java (Indonesia)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/222116_1b66febf30bff2910885271680fc34f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F222116_1b66febf30bff2910885271680fc34f7.jpg&h=1b8bef4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLake Toba (Indonesia)"},{"pid":"0075455a9d6f49558daa7587af4fa468cbe07f0a","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLF012G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLF012G.jpg&h=d7508888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬來西亞 檳城<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LtBZ3LX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtBZ3LX.jpg&h=3f574982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柬埔寨 吳哥窟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8CzAV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8CzAV2.jpg&h=6bcefc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國清邁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DqAN8K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DqAN8K.jpg&h=794195b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雲南麗江"},{"pid":"25dc53dd774f3e4b0d93e2d5926a82fd61b02832","tid":22624,"uid":13129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"老撾正呀"},{"pid":"7bbb76d5ceb8eee5deb2f30f37bf78173ffc4390","tid":22624,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"新加坡都冇去點算去過東南亞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d9011d46dea1a0f93a2a1b9f5b5de03bf97ef2","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老撾正呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係老撾冇乜點影相，因為呢個地方純樸到我唔想拎部手機出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a1c6c7d30761597bfdfce529021d44a6dd4855","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新加坡都冇去點算去過東南亞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚唔知新加坡係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係主觀覺得佢好都市化所以冇去 以後有機會（或者有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）會去睇下"},{"pid":"50d52e23c03b077892d89a1c6dcecb5183b766f4","tid":22624,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新加坡都冇去點算去過東南亞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚唔知新加坡係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係主觀覺得佢好都市化所以冇去 以後有機會（或者有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）會去睇下</blockquote><br />\n係呢 咁你大馬除左penang仲去左邊度?"},{"pid":"094ef07659764fd4d759ed7f61005515bc9bfac9","tid":22624,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新加坡都冇去點算去過東南亞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚唔知新加坡係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係主觀覺得佢好都市化所以冇去 以後有機會（或者有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）會去睇下</blockquote><br />\n係呢 咁你大馬除左penang仲去左邊度?</blockquote><br />\n唔去JB唔當去過大馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fbeb83269af406050b0d122c111524e2ce1b28","tid":22624,"uid":1941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:13:59.000Z","msg":"洗左幾多錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52398dbe1ac6e5239a91dec8f079c65f8ae5973","tid":22624,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"印尼去左邊D地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最鍾意邊個國家呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7159a553589e147d403cdcf6facff1bc756a134","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新加坡都冇去點算去過東南亞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚唔知新加坡係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係主觀覺得佢好都市化所以冇去 以後有機會（或者有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）會去睇下</blockquote><br />\n係呢 咁你大馬除左penang仲去左邊度?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吉隆坡<br />\n<br />\n其實我成個trip都係亂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  通常去下首都/出名啲嘅城市"},{"pid":"ea8fc060e2a5376b3131c59652375da81b74c415","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新加坡都冇去點算去過東南亞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚唔知新加坡係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係主觀覺得佢好都市化所以冇去 以後有機會（或者有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）會去睇下</blockquote><br />\n係呢 咁你大馬除左penang仲去左邊度?</blockquote><br />\n唔去JB唔當去過大馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有機會會去睇下"},{"pid":"ef88bd4adcfea5cd39ea1b8d7465beb0d588300a","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗左幾多錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我冇計 不過我估用唔過$20000？ 當中包括咗冤枉錢（遲啲再講）"},{"pid":"619996cb4c828e8beb1dffb288cf1f0813d45b92","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印尼去左邊D地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最鍾意邊個國家呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印尼去咗 Bali (Denpasar, Ubud), Bondowoso, Surabaya, Medan (Lake Toba)<br />\n <br />\n最鍾意泰國，不過其實每個國家都有好有壞"},{"pid":"cc0dc945053b048f80b50fc56c41d520eaad9a04","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:07:53.000Z","msg":"由於用手機打嘅關係，我會一張圖一段字咁打，方便啲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/06/155328_0542f775a135cd0f600c7ef4dfcc5922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F155328_0542f775a135cd0f600c7ef4dfcc5922.jpg&h=ef33cc1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人去旅行指定動作，我係有做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我已經cut咗我個頭出嚟。6月20日，旅程正式開始。<br />\n<br />\n之前book機票去峇里，我深明，我冇嘅係錢，有嘅係時間，所以我book咗Airasia由香港飛去吉隆坡，再由吉隆坡飛去峇里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 單程好似大約$700 啱啱search返skyscanner，呢個價錢好似算平？<br />\n<br />\n（其實香港係有直航機飛去峇里，國泰、香港航空都有，不過單程平日都要幾千蚊，所以完全冇考慮空間。）<br />\n<br />\n結果飛去吉隆坡之後，係吉隆坡機場逗留咗六個鍾，終於可以再飛去峇里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朝早上機，夜晚終於到印尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講開又講，由香港搭去馬來西亞，都仲有好多香港人嘅陪伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由馬來西亞去峇里個程開始，直至成個旅程完結，我哋居然完全遇唔到一個香港人。<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"bb0ead55d3a8a556b5ec5004e83f44eccf72d1d5","tid":22624,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"完?"},{"pid":"a49a94769725d5481f13a45b26520dd772a79729","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抱歉，前排有啲嘢發生咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家會重新振作繼續出遊記！請各位多多支持。"},{"pid":"48a6224a75e0a4c5a3a687820a27d3eb4778566c","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"呢間舖頭係我峇厘島印象最深刻嘅一間餐廳 Waroeng Kotobuki，外表毫不起眼，望到你完全唔會想行入去食。可能就係緣份，咁啱住個頭得呢間開緊，就入咗去食，食完十分有驚喜，又唔貴，自此留係峇厘島個幾日都瘋狂走去食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d4mqgo29\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd4mqgo29&h=5954a1da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我最鍾意食嘅就係佢個炒河粉，少少油膩，但對我嚟講係啱啱好。<br />\n<br />\n其中一晚係個度食飯嘅時候，個日好熱鬧，但神奇地佢廚師得一個。礙於個次應該係最後一次機會食呢間嘢，我同我朋友嗌咗好多嘢食，個唯一一個廚房師傅就一直Keep住剩係整我哋點嘅餸。<br />\n<br />\n後來有一對印度夫婦嚟到，遲過我哋落單。由於個廚房師傅要整哂我哋啲嘢食先，印度夫婦等到好唔耐煩，就開始問個侍應姐姐做乜要等咁耐。於是我哋同個姐姐講，其實可以出咗佢哋啲餸先，我哋可以一邊食一邊等。個侍應姐姐居然十分感激我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到我覺得自己好似捐咗十萬八萬咁。<br />\n<br />\n係香港我一定唔會咁做，我會覺得唔公平，我落單先自然應該煮咗我嘅嘢先，但唔知點解去旅行會就好似變咗一個人咁⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔知自己想講咩。多謝各位再次睇我鳩up。"},{"pid":"d26ca818fe64b449d318ad54740e72f8d7da3ee9","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:15:39.000Z","msg":"另外一提，因為係Lihkg up相有啲唔方便，每次可能只會up少少圖。如果想睇多啲圖可以去我fb page <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rakurakurakuuu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frakurakurakuuu%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KigT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=0e5b39e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rakurakurakuuu/</a>"},{"pid":"c25a71af7f0d4e02a4d0402dc1b1578da1a672a2","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"你哋又有冇係峇厘島食過啲好難忘嘅嘢食？"},{"pid":"c8733a2a2007f0af407a20f1e238e777128e15f9","tid":22624,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:39:51.000Z","msg":"留名! 二月頭會去印尼"},{"pid":"86ba70cd27d1b2134d6301a6d77621c39cb9a50c","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"我都知我更新速度好慢，但希望keep住會有人睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94f597c79eaec2680d64a20a85956133c8728a7","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/umohqg58\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fumohqg58&h=dcee8539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好，今日講下峇厘島嘅沙灘。注意純粹個人意見，唔同意勿屌。<br />\n<br />\n上圖係一個係庫塔Kuta嘅一個沙灘，畀我嘅感覺係好多遊客好熱鬧。可能係我出發前對峇厘島期望太高，嚟到嘅時候有少少失落，因為冇想像中咁靚，只不過呢個沙灘嘅海岸線(?)好長，但其實香港有好多沙灘都靚過佢。而令我有少少反感嘅，係見到有當地人直接係沙灘上面吐痰。本來眼不見為淨⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n不過其實我只係去咗峇厘島呢個係Kuta嘅沙灘，我相信係峇厘島其他遠少少嘅沙灘，應該係真係好靚嘅，如果唔係，Bali都唔會咁出名。<br />\n<br />\n所幸嘅係，臨離開峇厘最後一日，我哋又心血來潮想去個沙灘又玩一玩。一來轉咗酒店，間酒店離沙灘近好多。二來，個陣諗唔到有咩做，就話不如去沙灘瞓下覺。<br />\n<br />\n結果畀我影張咗我自己覺得好好睇嘅相。<br />\n<br />\n（因為會畀人認到，所以就唔up啦。）<br />\n<br />\n兩條傻仔其實係咁係個夕陽下面跑同跳，希望影張可以呃下like嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實峇厘島嘅夕陽係唔差嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9atc503n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9atc503n&h=a996e29e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗰一刻嘅夕陽真係好靚，但原諒我攝影技術未到家，呈現唔到嗰種震撼嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d91b00de8fc25b504d0cc6f63f3eee523c7048","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名! 二月頭會去印尼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完up上連登一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a88f696e44466fdcb26942ce42fa90e5760d468","tid":22624,"uid":58970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"有冇去過寮國？<br />\n未聽過有人去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a0a4e5131b9404bc94540e7ec9c84345dbad74","tid":22624,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇去過寮國？<br />\n未聽過有人去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩舊年十一月去過"},{"pid":"dd288f97d1ea1b95c893b451abd257dce46f1f17","tid":22624,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名! 二月頭會去印尼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完up上連登一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店你覺得住庫塔好定烏布好?"},{"pid":"ee5c81dc563d92a370d3cbe8d9abe6bd2b6aeed3","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇去過寮國？<br />\n未聽過有人去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啊，寮國即係老撾。去咗龍坡邦，好多外國人，特別係韓國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實背包客棧有好多關於老撾可以參考下。至於我自己去嘅遊記再遲啲再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450e9c81f35f05cdfe98710bc3133ab0b0558055","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名! 二月頭會去印尼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完up上連登一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店你覺得住庫塔好定烏布好?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇話邊度特別好，其實可以幾日住庫塔，幾日住烏布。個人覺得，庫塔比較熱鬧，烏布比較靜少少。庫塔有沙灘，烏布冇。<br />\n<br />\n由庫塔搭Perama Bus去烏布都只係個幾鐘車程，絕對可以即日來回。你自己再考慮下啦，希望幫到你"},{"pid":"164eadf6678aa5f5285a2096ed2568dd5e95df9c","tid":22624,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名! 二月頭會去印尼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完up上連登一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店你覺得住庫塔好定烏布好?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇話邊度特別好，其實可以幾日住庫塔，幾日住烏布。個人覺得，庫塔比較熱鬧，烏布比較靜少少。庫塔有沙灘，烏布冇。<br />\n<br />\n由庫塔搭Perama Bus去烏布都只係個幾鐘車程，絕對可以即日來回。你自己再考慮下啦，希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\nOK! 咁你有無去睇梯田? 應該由烏布去近D?"},{"pid":"ce69903767a32fb3d0293f4e1804244b330e9277","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nzk5m30i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnzk5m30i&h=8bb4b0d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBemo亡命之旅<br />\n<br />\n先解釋下咩係Bemo。其實類似的士，極殘舊嘅的士，搵到人一齊搭順風車可以Share車費。但我強烈建議外國旅客（除非好有經驗）唔好搭Bemo，因為佢會劏到你一勁血。<br />\n<br />\n本身冇諗住搭Bemo，因為知道其實幾危險下。去烏布個朝，原本諗住搭的士去Perama Bus間公司，再搭車直達烏布，價錢平又快，而且有好多外國人搭。但唔知點解最後的士大哥車咗我哋去一個車站，好偏僻嘅車站，天真嘅我以為，唔通係度等車？咁就一直等，逐架車問，去唔去到烏布？<br />\n<br />\n架架車都話No，終於有一架，個售票姐姐話轉車去到，嘩，當堂勁開心，以為搵啱巴士，但事實原來係笨柒咗，個㗎只不過係普通公共巴士。<br />\n<br />\n搭咗好耐，去到一個唔知咩嘅地方之後。個售票姐姐叫我哋搭Bemo去烏布。又話轉車去到，原來係轉Bemo！由於唔知大約價錢，個陣個Bemo司機講咗一個價錢，我哋轉返港紙覺得接受到就上咗車。但我哋後尾發現個價錢原來係貴過由庫塔搭Perama Bus去烏布！！！<br />\n<br />\n坐住個架好似就嚟散，而個車門又唔閂嘅Bemo，我有一刻覺得自己唔會返到香港⋯⋯但，都可以當係一個特別體驗嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實各位係可以試下搭Bemo㗎，但記住殺價。另外，之後會有一次被逼再搭Bemo嘅經歷，各位敬請期待。"},{"pid":"cc1ae97827161e996bedb358a146336907d33525","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名! 二月頭會去印尼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完up上連登一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店你覺得住庫塔好定烏布好?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇話邊度特別好，其實可以幾日住庫塔，幾日住烏布。個人覺得，庫塔比較熱鬧，烏布比較靜少少。庫塔有沙灘，烏布冇。<br />\n<br />\n由庫塔搭Perama Bus去烏布都只係個幾鐘車程，絕對可以即日來回。你自己再考慮下啦，希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\nOK! 咁你有無去睇梯田? 應該由烏布去近D?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇去睇梯田啊，行程有啲走馬看花，好多嘢都Miss咗"},{"pid":"dac80c296eacfeadb8c377c229d01f9202896a38","tid":22624,"uid":18926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:40:43.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973b9244b2afb6965ff603ad9c98dc383d949b53","tid":22624,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名! 二月頭會去印尼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完up上連登一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店你覺得住庫塔好定烏布好?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇話邊度特別好，其實可以幾日住庫塔，幾日住烏布。個人覺得，庫塔比較熱鬧，烏布比較靜少少。庫塔有沙灘，烏布冇。<br />\n<br />\n由庫塔搭Perama Bus去烏布都只係個幾鐘車程，絕對可以即日來回。你自己再考慮下啦，希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\nOK! 咁你有無去睇梯田? 應該由烏布去近D?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇去睇梯田啊，行程有啲走馬看花，好多嘢都Miss咗</blockquote><br />\n咁你係巴里去左邊D景點?"},{"pid":"0dbbb093b395441ebe1defcc1dbba00656d6da9a","tid":22624,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c142db60cbf8d0c198f7bf1869ef8ca8c83bfc50","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名! 二月頭會去印尼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去完up上連登一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店你覺得住庫塔好定烏布好?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇話邊度特別好，其實可以幾日住庫塔，幾日住烏布。個人覺得，庫塔比較熱鬧，烏布比較靜少少。庫塔有沙灘，烏布冇。<br />\n<br />\n由庫塔搭Perama Bus去烏布都只係個幾鐘車程，絕對可以即日來回。你自己再考慮下啦，希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\nOK! 咁你有無去睇梯田? 應該由烏布去近D?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇去睇梯田啊，行程有啲走馬看花，好多嘢都Miss咗</blockquote><br />\n咁你係巴里去左邊D景點?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f7e2e4b51ff5532c05da4d43673c6d3bdfaf9e","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/efhsdmrb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fefhsdmrb&h=15560121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一次講到我去咗烏布，咁跟住落嚟我就講下我係烏布食咗啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n其實一落到車，你已經感覺到呢度其實又係一個遊客區，因為周圍都係勁有度假Feel嘅餐廳，就好似上圖咁。不過其實呢個地方幾適合畀度假嚟發下呆，環境非常舒適。<br />\n<br />\n我哋分別食咗兩間唔同嘅餐廳，賣相可以，味道就一般，唔推介啦（因為我都唔記得咗佢哋叫咩名）。如果各位有推介嘅餐廳，可以留言分享下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o4b90fzk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo4b90fzk&h=974e6247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海鮮冬陰功麵 - 啲海鮮唔新鮮，但個湯幾好飲。個麵係公仔麵⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rhp9n0xe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frhp9n0xe&h=e010bae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係冬陰功 - 睇個樣都知唔好味，唔講了。<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家去我個page支持下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rakurakurakuuu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frakurakurakuuu&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KigT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=89998f3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rakurakurakuuu</a>"},{"pid":"1da0f91d1eb17bbb955129fe6726d3f4d29d6d10","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:44:07.000Z","msg":"其實我哋去烏布主要有兩樣嘢想做，就係學瑜珈同埋去Sacred Monkey Forest Sanctuary。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wjv7hsy0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwjv7hsy0&h=d88d36f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間就係瑜珈學校The Yoga Barn啦，環境又係非常舒適<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.theyogabarn.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theyogabarn.com%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KigT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=0e2e8b06\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.theyogabarn.com/</a> 順便畀埋條link大家（唔係賣廣告）<br />\n<br />\n之前係香港都有學開瑜珈，所以想體驗下係其他地方嘅瑜珈又係點嘅呢？而當搵峇厘島必做嘅事時，又有好多人推介去體驗下學瑜珈，所以就求奇搵咗呢間The Yoga Barn上咗一堂Yin Yoga。結果又真係唔錯，可能因為係香港學瑜珈係係冷氣地方，畀石屎森林包圍。而係烏布，你上堂嘅時候，係聽到雀仔聲，呼吸到新鮮空氣，所以感覺真係好特別。我極度推介大家如果去Bali記住去The Yoga Barn上返堂。另外，唔洗擔心聽唔明，因為導師英文好流暢。<br />\n<br />\n講多一講，The Yoga Barn唔像一間學校，從上圖睇得出，佢完全又係度假feel，所以坐下又係幾寫意。<br />\n<br />\n跟住講下Sacred Monkey Forest Sanctuary，未入到去，已經有好多隻馬騮係度搞鳩你⋯⋯友人因為太過驚，我哋結果冇入去⋯⋯"},{"pid":"b5ea4cb8abece617698e936b0ec9e4335039788c","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:57:06.000Z","msg":"你哋每一個留言，都係我打文嘅動力嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51fc5829e54a35e2678754536ced2d4c3a29702","tid":22624,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"好想搵人同我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留個靚名物"},{"pid":"7ce3163a4030b5069958f56e054669ad517ae329","tid":22624,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想搵人同我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留個靚名先</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5d4e395a9b787a9fe2ba3efbbf7db0b364bed7ab","tid":22624,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你哋每一個留言，都係我打文嘅動力嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有你d印尼紙係香港唱定，去到當地機場先唱？"},{"pid":"5180cc55e739d2d9f67694c4268a9e42216672f8","tid":22624,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85ced82cc92de6976659ede8df5ae31056268e7","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你哋每一個留言，都係我打文嘅動力嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有你d印尼紙係香港唱定，去到當地機場先唱？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係香港唱咗大部分，用港紙唱印尼盾應該係香港唱抵啲。因為我係去好多日，我驚帶太多錢係身唔安全，所以好多時候都會選擇㩒錢"},{"pid":"5d6e74393c9b3e56fac6f7f2eeb73c33d1de30b8","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"2002年，峇里島庫塔地區發生恐怖襲擊，造成202人死亡，209人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hbpmwdek\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhbpmwdek&h=77f1fcaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同朋友其實冇特登去搵呢個紀念碑，只係有一日係庫塔酒吧區行緊嘅時候，咁啱見到佢。<br />\n<br />\n成個感覺好奇怪，紀念碑會令你散發一種哀傷嘅情緒，但係同時間四方八方你又畀成條街熱鬧嘅酒吧包圍住，有種好唔舒服嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n另外一提，庫塔鬧區真係大部分都係遊客，如果係想感受當地文化，我建議唔需要擺太多時間落庫塔，因為印尼其實有更加多值得去嘅地方。"},{"pid":"e6ba5758253fb84f19c3dd44c139e6606ec482eb","tid":22624,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3ef078f0266af42aadcba420fe8eeb847c74687","tid":22624,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"屌！終於到日惹<br />\nDelay 成四個鐘終於到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c9ad55644604c9c842bc811d63abb033a155cd","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"去東南亞旅行，我梗係唔去啲開畀遊客食嘅貴價餐廳度食飯。我覺得旅行就係要食下當地人平時會食嘅嘢，先可以認識多啲佢哋嘅文化。<br />\n<br />\n有一日我哋去咗Bus Terminal Ubung（至於點解會去，等陣再講），一個終於冇乜遊客嘅地方。買完車飛有啲肚餓，我哋就順便係附近食埋dinner，於是我哋又是但入咗間聞落幾香嘅小餐館食飯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m3ais5gp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm3ais5gp&h=a1c499ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢冇英文餐牌，其實嘢食係隨便叫嘅，好似食車仔麵咁。如圖，有一個玻璃櫃，擺住各種食材，想食咩就指點，佢幫你加埋一齊煮。<br />\n<br />\n出於溝通上嘅問題，出嚟嘅同我想像嘅有好大分別。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ekb3zvyn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fekb3zvyn&h=3fed5980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要啦，都幾好味，幾有家的味道。"},{"pid":"8e71f5dcf395eb799cf77d6d2bf9b9b95afe4d28","tid":22624,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解有咁多日假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我仲係學生，暑假嗰陣去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}